node.text:
This Feta pasta is one of the easist ways to make a delcious, cheap week night dinner - here are 3 ways to do it AND the full ingridients list, because we love you x

Follow @twisted for more recipes!

INGREDIENTS
Feta pasta a la vodka
 
1 block feta cheese
500g cherry tomatoes
3-4 garlic cloves 
½ cup olive oil
½ tsp chilli flakes
Pepper to taste
50ml vodka
500g cooked tagliatelle
Grated fresh parmegiano reggiano cheese
Fresh basil for garnish
 
 
Grilled Chicken & pesto Gnocchi
 
1 block feta cheese
500g cherry tomatoes
3-4 garlic cloves 
½ cup olive oil
½ tsp chilli flakes
Pepper to taste
3 chicken breasts, grilled and sliced
½ cup pesto
500g gnocchi, cooked
Toasted pine nuts
Grated parmesan cheese
 
Spinach Canneloni
 
1 block feta cheese
500g cherry tomatoes
3-4 garlic cloves 
½ cup olive oil
½ tsp chilli flakes
Pepper to taste
500g cooked chopped spinach
½ tsp ground nutmeg
6 lasagna noodles, par-cooked
Grated mozzarella
Chopped parsley
#fetapasta #fetacheesepasta #yummyrecipe #fetapastachallenge

* 	Basil, to serve

This recipe is the perfect dessert for you! 

COOKIE DOUGH MOUSSE CAKE
INGREDIENTS
Cookie Dough:
¾ cups butter, softened
¾ cup brown sugar
¼ cup granulated sugar
1 ½ cups flour
1 tsp salt
1 tsp vanilla
2 tsp milk
1 cup chocolate chips
Mousse:
200g dark chocolate, chopped fine
3/4 cup whipping cream, hot
2 1/4 cup whipping cream, cold
1 tsp vanila
2 tbsp icing sugar
2 cups heavy cream, hot
454g dark chocolate finely chopped

125g plain flour

125ml whole milk
63 ml vegetable oil
1 large egg
1 tsp vanilla extract
125ml boiling water
1 1/2 cups heavy cream

575g cream cheese, softened to room temperature

250ml heavy cream

125g milk chocolate finely chopped
100g dark chocolate finely chopped
Finely chopped peanuts and chocolate shavings

node.text:
This Feta pasta is one of the easist ways to make a delcious, cheap week night dinner - here are 3 ways to do it AND the full ingridients list, because we love you x

Follow @twisted for more recipes!

INGREDIENTS
Feta pasta a la vodka
 
1 block feta cheese
500g cherry tomatoes
3-4 garlic cloves 
½ cup olive oil
½ tsp chilli flakes
Pepper to taste
50ml vodka
500g cooked tagliatelle
Grated fresh parmegiano reggiano cheese
Fresh basil for garnish
 
 
Grilled Chicken & pesto Gnocchi
 
1 block feta cheese
500g cherry tomatoes
3-4 garlic cloves 
½ cup olive oil
½ tsp chilli flakes
Pepper to taste
3 chicken breasts, grilled and sliced
½ cup pesto
500g gnocchi, cooked
Toasted pine nuts
Grated parmesan cheese
 
Spinach Canneloni
 
1 block feta cheese
500g cherry tomatoes
3-4 garlic cloves 
½ cup olive oil
½ tsp chilli flakes
Pepper to taste
500g cooked chopped spinach
½ tsp ground nutmeg
6 lasagna noodles, par-cooked
Grated mozzarella
Chopped parsley
#fetapasta #fetacheesepasta #yummyrecipe #fetapastachallenge

These balls are heavenly! 🧀 
CROQUE MONSIEUR MASH BALLS
INGREDIENTS 👇👇👇
* 	6 cups cold leftover mash
* 	4 slices ham, chopped into small cubes
* 	3 cups grated emmental
* 	2 tbsp dijon mustard
* 	1/4 cup finely chopped parsley
* 	1 tbsp salt
* 	1 tbsp pepper
* 	1 cup flour
* 	4 eggs, beaten with a little milk
* 	2 cups panko breadcrumbs
* 	Enough groundnut oil to deep fry

node.text:
This recipe really takes the biscuit!

BLACK FOREST GATEAUX ICE BOX CAKE
INGREDIENTS
* 	300g rectangular chocolate sandwich biscuits 
* 	4 cups tinned cherries
* 	1/2 cup water
* 	3/4 cup sugar
* 	2 tbsp cornstarch
* 	800l double cream
* 	200g cream cheese
* 	100g icing sugar
* 	200g dark chocolate
* 	200g milk chocolate
* 	300ml double cream
* 	800ml double cream
* 	50ml icing sugar
* 	Fresh cherries, to serve
* 	Chopped chocolate, to serve

 #delicious #foodgoals #nobakedessert #chocolatecake #noleftovers

CHICKEN PARM DEEP DISH PIZZA
INGREDIENTS
* 	8 chicken breasts
* 	150g plain flour
* 	4 eggs
* 	200g breadcrumbs
* 	50g parmesan
* 	1 tsp Italian seasoning
 
* 	1 tbsp olive oil
* 	3 cloves of garlic, diced
* 	1/2 tsp chilli flakes
* 	1l tomato passata
* 	1 onion
* 	20g butter
* 	1 tsp salt
* 	1 tsp sugar
 
* 	140ml warm water
* 	1 tsp instant yeast
* 	1 tbsp granulated sugar
* 	2 tbsp olive oil
* 	1/2 tsp salt
* 	225g bread flour
 
* 	200g mozzarella, sliced
* 	750g parmesan, grated
* 	Basil, to serve

This recipe is the perfect dessert for you! 

COOKIE DOUGH MOUSSE CAKE
INGREDIENTS
Cookie Dough:
¾ cups butter, softened
¾ cup brown sugar
¼ cup granulated sugar
1 ½ cups flour
1 tsp salt
1 tsp vanilla
2 tsp milk
1 cup chocolate chips
Mousse:
200g dark chocolate, chopped fine
3/4 cup whipping cream, hot
2 1/4 cup whipping cream, cold
1 tsp vanila
2 tbsp icing sugar
2 cups heavy cream, hot
454g dark chocolate finely chopped
